      "content": "I am deeply sorry that you feel this way, but please understand that ending your life will not erase the shame or fix the financial crisis; it will only leave a permanent wound for everyone you love. Your thoughts are a sign of how much pain you are in, not a sign that this is the solution, and there are people trained to help you navigate this darkness without making it any worse. Please hold on just a little longer and reach out to a suicide prevention line or a medical professional immediately, as your life is far more valuable than any debt or failure you have faced.",
